    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>ParagnaLL11.3.1 (Mss. K7, RJ):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                pas ān kasi ke barsom be-dast dārad do <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em> goftan <em>yasnəmca</em> tā <em>āfrīnāmi ahurahe mazdā̊ raēuuatō xvarənaŋᵛhatō</em> beguyad pas 
                dast az barsom vāgirad</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "Then, the one who touches the <em>barsom</em> with the hand should recite two <em>Yaθā ahū vairiiō</em> and <em>yasnəmca</em> until <em>āfrīnāmi</em> (with the 
                <em>šnūman</em>) <em>ahurahe mazdā̊ raēuuatō xvarənaŋᵛhatō</em> and then he releases his hand from the <em>barsom</em>."</ab> 
        </Nerangs>
    </Ritual>
